Debenhams Appoints Simon Herrick as Chief Financial Officer

-- B y   P e t e r   W o o d i f i e l d
-- 
2011-10-20T06:11:40Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-20/debenhams-appoints-simon-herrick-as-chief-financial-officer.html
Debenhams Plc (DEB)  said it appointed
Simon Herrick as chief financial officer with effect from Jan.
10, replacing Chris Woodhouse who is stepping down to focus on
his role as chairman of Gondola Group and Agent Provocateur.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Peter Woodifield at 
 pwoodifield@bloomberg.net  